name: TRACEUR 01
description:
Parkour practitioners are called traceur if they are men or traceuse if they are women, terms derived from the French verb tracer.
with this work I wanted to represent the state in which we all enter thanks to this platform, although I rely on my pillars that are vaporwave and cyberpunk, I did not want to stop evoking the feeling that transmits me to be working on a platform like this one.
